snippet.title: 🔴FIT FRESH AND FANTASTIC EPISODE 1 LIVE WITH AMBER GOT THE JUICE
snippet.description:
Fit Fresh and Fantastic
Live Interview show on health wellness fitness and freshness.
We have Yogis, Personal Trainers, Business Owners Doctors in the Fitness and Health Industries.
#AmberGotTheJuice #FitFreshAndFantastic
Subscribe and Hit the 🛎 for all Notifications and Live Shows
https://www.youtube.com/c/JalikTheLeader

Smash the Like Button and Share Your Thoughts

JalikTheLeader@gmail.com
Jalik TheLeader on all Social Media

Check out Ambers Story and Business:
https://ambergotthejuice.com/

Juicing helped to change my life….literally!  I am excited to share my journey of living a healthier life style with you.  I hope that by sharing my story, I can encourage you to become healthy with the ultimate goal of improving your quality of life. For years I struggled with defining Gods purpose for my life.  I knew that I enjoyed helping people, however I realized that I needed to narrow my focus, so I did a little soul searching to figure out the best way I could serve others.  My answer didn’t come quick, and needless to say I had no idea that I was about to embark on a journey that would shake me at my core. 

 More about that later….. 

 

I started juicing and creating smoothie recipes in 2013. Just for fun. I did this almost every day in my kitchen.  After about a year, I slowly got pulled away from my juicing ritual due to increasing demands from my job and a hectic work schedule.  I stopped juicing for almost a year.  I just could never find the time- 

 

In 2015, I starting having joint pains throughout my body, but I thought that it was due to me being tired, and that I just needed to stretch.  I also noticed that I was sleepy ALL THE TIME…even after getting 8 hours of sleep.  My pain increased and became so severe that it hurt for me to walk, sit, get up, flush the toilet, bathe, drive, open doors and get dressed.  Basically…every joint in my body hurt. 

 

After a year of going to several specialist including 3 different Rheumatologist, I finally got my diagnosis…rheumatoid arthritis. As you can imagine, to get this diagnosis at 26 years old, I was devastated.  I couldn’t understand how and why I developed this disease when there was no known history of it in my family.  

 

I was literally unhappy for months… but I didn’t stay there.  It was time to put ME first. I decided that I would fight. 

 

 I was determined to beat this disease, even though I was told that there was not a cure.  I started doing my research, and was amazed to learn about the link between diet and certain diseases. 

Then it suddenly came to me…..JUICING!!! So the BEAST reminded me of the BEAUTY of juicing. 

 

I am excited to report that my health has made a dramatic turnaround since I started back juicing and modifying my diet.   I am well on the way to putting my RA into remission—I no longer have joint pain. I am also proud to say that I found a passion…so let me help you discover your “healthier self” by trying out my delicious juices and smoothies. I am so thankful for all of your support and positive feedback.
